/**
 * Golden eval set — 200 representative customer messages across all intent categories.
 *
 * Categories:
 *   ready_to_buy (40)   — buying signals, cart help, checkout issues
 *   interested (40)     — product questions, comparisons, demo requests
 *   price_objection (30) — haggling, competitor pricing, discount requests
 *   inquiry (40)        — shipping, returns, policies, order status
 *   complaint (30)      — damage, wrong item, delayed shipment, bad experience
 *   other (20)          — off-topic, unclear, spam-adjacent
 *
 * Each case sets a passThreshold (judge score required to pass).
 * Complaint cases have a higher threshold (75) — tone matters more.
 */

